x Milo Blake for @truereligion 🩶

Motherhood is such a beautiful thing, and being Milos mom is the greatest title that I have ever possessed. Milo is truly my baby best friend, the funniest, kindest, sweetest most beautiful pure soul. We laugh all day, love on each other, and drive each other crazy, he holds me accountable, and has taught me so much. He’s so kind, so gentle, yet determined and so independent. It has been a journey, and although it’s not always easy, it’s always worth it. I am honored to be Milos mom, it is my purpose, my favorite thing about this life and I’m excited to share a bit about with you guys. 

Head to @truereligion for the full story. Use my code Tatiana10 to treat yourself or a special mother in your life. They deserve. #MYRLGN

got it from my mama ✨

Milo, my Mom, and I for @calvinklein eternity 🩶

My big boy is 3 today and I absolutely cannot believe it. 

It feels like yesterday finding out that I was pregnant, I instantly named you Milo, the day I found out lol. Feeling so scared, worried, I wanted to do all the right things eat all the right things, create the perfect environment for you to be able to thrive in, grow in, play in, laugh in love in.

I am so thankful for you, you’ve pushed me beyond limits of what I thought I could even accomplish and showed me what unconditional love is. I love our cuddles, we laugh so much, we play all day and you lowkey act like the parent at times. You’re so funny so sweet so smart, everyday spent with you is something new and so beautiful . Your sweet and pure spirit touches everyone around you, you exude love. You exude happiness. I’m so happy that I have the privilege of being your mom. It’s not always easy, but it’s always worth it. I can’t wait to see what greatness you accomplish because you truly are so special. I love you so so much, beyond words. I can’t believe you’re 3 years old. Happy Birthday Milo Blake 🤎🥹

Y’all, I can’t believe how big Milo is getting 🥹

He’s so independent, so funny, so loving, so polite, I catch him having conversations with himself and I crack up laughing like how can you even talk?!? He’s soooo independent and headstrong lol if I don’t get him what he asked for fast enough I turn around and he’s making a way to get it himself. He’s so shy and sweet and you really have to kiss up to him for him to like you 😂 he hates when I record him, I have to bribe him to take pictures with me even though he’s up under me 24/7 lol I love that he loves being a kid, all he wants to do is laugh, be loved on and play. I love being his mom more than anything in this world. I can’t believe how fast time is flying I want to cry everyday when I look at him and how pure his soul is. 🥹🤎

tbt.. I can’t believe I’ve been that girl, for this long jk💅🏽😂

Lol but seriously, I’m so thankful, scrolling down my own feed and reflecting on my own journey is always so fun for me. I’m lowkey inspired bc 2017 me is eating current me up lol 😂 

Im so so thankful for every follower, friend, brand & partnership that has supported me. Things looked a lot different in 2017, I remember being the only black girl in so many rooms. It’s such a blessing to be able to have learned this business, maintain, and evolve off something everyone looked at me crazy for😂 

If you’ve read this far and happen to be in LA I will be at @everystylishgirl this Saturday speaking on my experience as a Model, entrepreneur and content creator. come say hi 🤎
